msgid ""
"Here again, commands are rather straightforward (and <command>vgdisplay</"
"command> proposes two output formats). Note that it is quite possible to use "
"two partitions of the same physical disk into two different VGs. Note also "
"that we used a <filename>vg_</filename> prefix to name our VGs, but it is "
"nothing more than a convention."
msgstr ""
"در اینجا نیز دستورات واضح هستند و <command>vgdisplay</command> شامل دو قالب "
